{"Sid":0,"Did":118123,"Id":"282269","Title":"礁溪成功新村「沐德懷仁」碑、「恩同再造」碑、「惠及吾民」碑","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/4d694d2f-2d46-40fa-8e5d-795d737d4c57/108-her-pa-1804-201910252202195db2e16a5063c0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/622c8d76-834f-493d-8a2e-d3c65a210390/108-her-pa-1804-201910252202195db2e16a5063c1.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/8a1d011f-b8ca-4cc9-9539-865da9bfe6ee/108-her-pa-1804-201910252202195db2e16a5063c2.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n1955年2月8日至11日間，位於浙江台州的大陳列島居民因國共戰爭而撤退到台灣，在基隆港上岸並短暫停留後，即安置在全台12個縣市，建立35處大陳新村供大陳民眾居住。1年後的1956年2月8日，亦即大陳居民撤退來台一周年的日子，各地大陳新村共舉落成典禮。大陳人對於安全撤退到台灣來，生活雖困頓，但對撤退來台一事卻視為是愛國之舉並充滿感恩。在各個大陳新村中，均可見到頌揚政府德政的碑碣。 　　在礁溪成功新村入口處蔣中正塑像底座，除沿革碑外，尚嵌有三方的頌德碑。一面題以「恩同再造」，以感謝時任國防會議副秘書長的蔣經國；一面題以「惠及吾民」，以感謝時任台灣省主席的嚴家淦；一面則題以「沐德懷仁」，以感謝時任宜蘭縣長的甘阿炎。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7696964","Keyword_Latitude":"24.8214206","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/1A381B65-B54C-400F-9FDA-622D6F7A5AE6","Original_Identifier":"282269","Keyword_Subject_1":"社會與政治","alias":"","Keywords":"大陳 / 甘阿炎 / 成功新村 / 蔣經國 / 礁溪 / 嚴家淦","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:09:09","timelines":"","place":"礁溪鄉成功新村","address":"宜蘭縣礁溪鄉成功新村","longitude":"121.7696964","latitude":"24.8214206","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/4f5a50cb-39d8-48b8-a82c-1da94071e